data.description: This gorgeous renovated barn home on over 6 acres is quintessential country living just minutes from town.  Beautiful details and amazing natural light in every room.  Large primary bedroom with walk in closet and wood, track sliding door. 30x50 shop with 10x50 lean-to offers a loft, office space, 30 amp RV hookups in the shop and 50 amp in the shed.  Garden space on south facing lot is perfect for extending to a substantial size or building a greenhouse. Fully fenced pasture for your animals and cleared acreage ready for your dream barn or vineyard. Brand new carpet and HVAC system. Take your vision for this modern farmhouse to the next level with even more potential for living space with it's framed in upper level.
